- Lauren.
- Hi, George.

03:44.393 --> 03:47.513
- Have dinner with me tonight.
- What?

03:47.605 --> 03:51.554
- Say, "Yes."
- George.

03:51.650 --> 03:55.066
- Say, "Yes."
- Why are you acting like this?

03:56.363 --> 03:59.033
Because I wanna be with you.

03:59.116 --> 04:01.192
Well, that's nice.

04:03.496 --> 04:06.165
